<bibRefCitation author="Benedek" box="[639,822,1582,1607]" pageId="3" refString="Benedek, P. (1970) The semiaquatic Heteroptera in the Carpathian Basin with notes on the distribution and the phenology of the species. Faunistische Abhandlungen, 3 (6), 27 - 49." type="journal article" year="1970">
